# Auto-request GitHub Copilot Code Review on every PR.
#
# `*` covers every file; @copilot-pull-request-reviewer is the GitHub
# Copilot reviewer bot. The pattern ensures every PR gets a review
# request when opened, without needing to click "Reviewers → Copilot"
# manually.
#
# This is advisory, not a required reviewer: PRs can still merge if
# Copilot hasn't replied, since the review isn't a CI gate.

*  @copilot-pull-request-reviewer
